text: Good food  but officers are too harsh
Call many times, answering machine control...then after following machine instructions, no answers then voice mail box always full.....very frustrating..
Darul Ihsan Boys' Orphanage is managed by the Muslimin Trust Fund Association (MTFA). Kudos to the management and staff for taking good care of the residents here!
